script:
1). Would you mind if I smoke?
No, I didn't.
I'll get some water.
Yes, I'm afraid I would. 
2). Don't we have to sign in at the front desk?
The sign is over there.
Oh yes, I forgot. 
No, we haven't.
3). Weren't you going to call Helen back?
Yes I was. Thanks for reminding me. 
No, you weren't going to call Helen.
She sure was. I appreciate it.
